  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t国办1月6日发布通知，调整上海自贸区内相关行政法规。明确规定，允许外资企业从事游戏游艺设备的生产和销售，通过文化主管部门内容审查的游戏游艺设备可面向国内市场销售。这意味着我国自2000年起实施的游戏机禁售规定解除。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t1. What's your opinion of the news above?<br />\n\t2. Do you love to play games? What's your attitude towards games?</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tBack to 2000 A.D., &quot;for the good of our children&quot;, as it was explained, the &quot;concerned departments&quot; announced a ban on the production and sale of game consoles in Chinese mainland. After that, popular consoles like PSP, Xbox and Wii became <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/smuggle\" target=\"_blank\">smuggled</a> goods sold on gray markets for game fanciers. But the fact is, over the past 13 years, living in an increasingly <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/digital\" target=\"_blank\">digital</a> world, that children get easier access to game devices from computers to smartphones. For instance, today it is difficult to find a kid who has no idea of Angry Bird, or Plants Vs Zombies. Therefore, the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/abortion\" target=\"_blank\">abortion</a> of the ban is surely a good news for foreign companies like Sony, Microsoft and Nintendo. On the other hand, I believe that playing game is not as harmful as many adults think, who actually play more often. Moderate game playing helps children develop their creativity, imagination and reaction. The discussions on the ban of games bring us back to the admitted lesson that &quot;every coin has two sides&quot;, and now the autorities have just found the other side of it, wearing the glasses of needs for reform.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/864669/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p589310/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p589310\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p589579/\">美国18岁少女酷似真人芭比 网络爆红</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p589721/\">外媒看中国：《来自星星的你》火到了两会</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p589617/\">YouTube热门视频：有爱的陌生人初吻</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p547912/\">奶茶妹妹被爆恋京东掌门：哥大是个好地方</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590023/\">白色情人节汇总：说出一世的约定！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590061/\">卡梅伦首相送女儿上幼儿园 父女俩齐卖萌</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588794/\">法航447空难纪实：消失的法航447(视频)</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590086/\">李克强总理答中外记者问（口译现场）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590111/\">李克强总理答记者问精彩语录（双语） </a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
