  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p588102/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201403/e390204c54a648cda6aae88f2598d640.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\"><strong><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\">《英闻天天译》</a></strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">是一档沪江部落的原创翻译互动节目（</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(128, 0, 128);\"><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/item/885076/\"><strong>戳去参与节目&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">），主持人提供翻译参考文本，对大家递交的翻译作品进行点评，和大家共同进步！本期节目选取的是关于</span>招聘广场为招募者开启求职者大学功课模式<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 28px; font-family: verdana, helvetica;\">一则英文报道，让我们一起在翻译中关注</span><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</font></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>SUMMARY：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t招聘广场为招募者开启求职者大学功课模式</p>\n<div>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">CONTENT：</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPiazza, an online study network popular with college engineering students, wants to help tech <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/startup\" target=\"_blank\">startup</a>s <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/compete\" target=\"_blank\">compete</a> in the war for talent.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA new recruiting tool called Piazza Careers lets companies connect with potential job candidates among the more than one million students who use the site. The service, which has been available for a test period to a limited group of companies, opened to everyone today, Chief Executive Pooja Sankar said in an interview.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPiazza will charge <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/recruiter\" target=\"_blank\">recruiter</a>s a subscription fee, starting at $20,000 per school term, to search and message candidates on the site. Similar tools are offered by professional resume site LinkedIn. But Piazza's big advantage is its large base of top engineering students, a group that is largely absent from other job sites, said Keith Rabois, a Piazza investor who is also a former vice president at LinkedIn.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 100, 0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<strong><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\">【英闻天天译】</a></strong>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t一个名为&ldquo;求职广场&rdquo;的新生招聘网站已然面世，该网站可从数以百万计的学生用户中甄选出潜在求职者，并将其与公司接上线。网站董事长波亚&middot;桑卡尔在接受访问时称，测试期间此服务仅对部分公司开放，如今则面向大众全面公开。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &ldquo;广场&rdquo;将向招聘者征收订阅费用，价格为每学期两万美元起，该项费用用于寻找求职者并向其发送招聘信息。与之类似的网站还包括职业简历网站&mdash;&ldquo;商务化人际关系网&rdquo;。然而据&ldquo;广场&rdquo;投资者之一的基思&middot;拉波斯先生（此前基斯先生曾担任商务化人际关系网的副董事）称，&ldquo;广场&rdquo;的优势在于其庞大的工程专业学生群，而这亦是其它求职网站所欠缺的。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &ldquo;商务化人际关系网既无力吸引大批刚毕业的学生，又无法作为科技精英们默认的就业平台。&rdquo;基思先生如是说到。</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/item/885076/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p588102/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p588102\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p589579/\">美国18岁少女酷似真人芭比 网络爆红</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p589721/\">外媒看中国：《来自星星的你》火到了两会</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p589617/\">YouTube热门视频：有爱的陌生人初吻</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p547912/\">奶茶妹妹被爆恋京东掌门：哥大是个好地方</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590023/\">白色情人节汇总：说出一世的约定！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590061/\">卡梅伦首相送女儿上幼儿园 父女俩齐卖萌</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588794/\">法航447空难纪实：消失的法航447(视频)</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590086/\">李克强总理答中外记者问（口译现场）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p590111/\">李克强总理答记者问精彩语录（双语） </a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
